snippet.title: HIDDEN CAVERN from the DARKEST DEPTHS Dungeon - Beneath the Nexus
snippet.description:
https://aced.gg/
https://playbtn.com/

Preview of Darkest Depths' Hidden Cavern area, where you'll encounter the Eye of the Monstrosity. As always, there's still tons of work to be done before we're finished with this section of the dungeon.

Video music from HeatleyBros @ (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SY-49rIbOSc). They are fantastic!
